{"tid":1818391,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃色經濟冇用架］香港電視交易額，全年持平，第四季按年升39%","createTime":"2020-01-10T01:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T01:41:26.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65c80cb3143b32702f369fdb0ed99d220ec5d2b4","tid":1818391,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:10:51.000Z","msg":"【財華社訊】香港電視(01137-HK)公佈，截至2019年12月31日止年度，集團網購平台及門市(HKTVmall及HoKoBuy)全年訂單總商品交易額為27.8億港元，較去年持平。<br />\n<br />\n於2019年10月、11月及12月，平均每日訂單數量分别為1.87萬、1.81萬及1.95萬，分别同比增長53.28%、48.36%及51.16%;平均訂單值分别為467港元、459港元及456港元；每月訂單總商品交易額分别為2.71億港元、2.50億港元及2.76億港元，分别同比增長38.97%、37.36%及41.54%。<br />\n<br />\n四季度訂單總商品交易額合計為7.97億港元，按年上升39.34%。<br />\n<br />\n此外，董事會訂立集團之電子商貿業務2020年財務年度全年訂單量總商品交易額目標為33.8億港元，按年增長 21.6%，視乎現時社會事件及經濟狀況的發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.finet.hk/newscenter/news_content/5e16efa3bde0b34b477090ed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.finet.hk%2Fnewscenter%2Fnews_content%2F5e16efa3bde0b34b477090ed&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=01bfc778\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.finet.hk/newscenter/news_content/5e16efa3bde0b34b477090ed</a><br />\n<br />\n一定唔關黃色經濟事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1503ed105c3f13760803c0e60fb20271b19bcc5f","tid":1818391,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:13:14.000Z","msg":"邊撚度係較去年持平?<br />\n係升40%<br />\n同目標持平阿"},{"pid":"8a5da902d776f84f7b2173a23ba3daed97837ee8","tid":1818391,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1503ed105c3f13760803c0e60fb20271b19bcc5f","tid":1818391,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:13:14.000Z","msg":"邊撚度係較去年持平?<br />\n係升40%<br />\n同目標持平阿"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T01:19:38.000Z","msg":"全年總數持平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係前三季應該